{"id": "art-25129", "label": "Art. 25129", "title": "Art. 25129", "slug": "art-25129", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1887896379\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1631\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1887896379\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>29</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2084967974\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1630\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2084967974\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\nfiec&#259;rei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> participante la\nfuziune, luând <span class=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span>, dac&#259;\neste cazul, de rapoartele prev&#259;zute la art. 251<sup>25</sup> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>26</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>,\ndup&#259; caz, de <span class=SpellE>observa&#355;iile</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau ale <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde proiectul de fuziune transfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde opinia cu privire la raportul destinat acestora, formulat&#259; potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>25</sup>, <span\nclass=SpellE>hot&#259;r&#259;&#351;te</span> asupra proiectului comun de\nfuziune transfrontalier&#259;. Prevederile art. 116 se aplic&#259; în mod\ncorespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_421451162\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1629\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_421451162\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ie</span> de la\nprevederile art. 117 alin. (2) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ale art. 195\nalin. (3), termenul de întrunire al adun&#259;rii generale a <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> nu poate fi mai mic de <span class=SpellE>&#351;ase</span>\ns&#259;pt&#259;mâni de la data convoc&#259;rii acesteia, potrivit <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2026709029\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1628\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2026709029\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în\ncomandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, hot&#259;rârea se\nadopt&#259; potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 115\nalin. (2) teza a doua, prin actul constitutiv neputând fi stabilite <span\nclass=SpellE>cerin&#355;e</span> de majoritate mai mari de 90% din voturile <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> de <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span> sau <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_119721785\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1627\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_119721785\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259;, hot&#259;rârea se adopt&#259; cu cvorumul\nprev&#259;zut la art. 192, dar cu o majoritate de cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\ndou&#259; treimi din voturile <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span> sau <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>,\nprin actul constitutiv neputând fi stabilite <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;e</span>\nde majoritate mai mari de 90% din voturile <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>.</span></p>"}